# 🧠 Core Effect Pipeline

## `add_effect()`

All effects eventually enter:

```
Effect Source
      ↓
EffectManager
      ↓
Resolve Target
      ↓
Apply Immediate Effect
      ↓
Register Active Effect
      ↓
StatManager / Tick System
```

