# 🌍 Difficulty Integration

Difficulty scaling is implemented as a passive effect.

This allows difficulty changes to use the same system as:

* Equipment bonuses
* Buffs
* Debuffs
* Class passives

Example:

```
Difficulty: Nightmare

Passive Effect:
+25% Enemy Damage
+50% Enemy Health
+10% Enemy Speed
```

No separate difficulty modifier pipeline is required.

