## 💚 HOT

Healing over time.

Examples:

* Regeneration
* Healing aura
* Recovery fields

---

## 💀 REVIVE

Revival effect.

Supports:

* HP restoration
* MP restoration
* Class resource restoration

Can restore:

* Flat values
